author: 1UPminifig
title: Never can have to many of  these!
review:
I do not own this set, but I own a lot of white bricks

Since no one decided to review this set I thought I might as well do it. In this pack you get a hundred white squares for seven bucks,a pretty good deal. As always with Lego, the quality of the bricks are outstanding.
As you would expect theirs no playability to the "set", but you get what you payed for, a bunch of white squares for building what ever you want!
